
Prerequisites:

cmake, opencv


To compile in the lab
——————————

run ./lab_config.sh
cd build
make

To compile on your own machine
———

cd build/
cmake ../
make


To run
——

In the build folder:
./sc image1 new_width new_height image2

 

for the sobel derivatives used in project
[1]https://docs.opencv.org/2.4.13.4/doc/tutorials/imgproc/imgtrans/sobel_derivatives/sobel_derivatives.html